com.esri.mo2.map.core
Interface AcetateLayer

All Known Implementing Classes:
AcetateLayer, AcetateLayer
public interface AcetateLayer

An AcetateLayer is a layer that could be added to a Map object and sits on top of other map layers. It could be optionally associated with a map layer, usually in those cases that the AcetateLayer uses sub-set of the associated map layer.
